# GitHub Natural Language Commands

When the user says any of the following phrases, execute the corresponding action:

## Save/Push Commands

| User Says | Agent Action |
|-----------|--------------|
| "save to github" | Run `pnpm github:save` |
| "push to github" | Run `pnpm github:save` |
| "push changes" | Run `pnpm github:save` |
| "commit this" | Run `pnpm github:save` |
| "save my work" | Run `pnpm github:save` |
| "backup to github" | Run `pnpm github:save --message "backup"` |
| "commit with message X" | Run `pnpm github:save --message "X"` |

